{"tid":598162,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"布偶貓一問","createTime":"2018-03-19T09:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T12:16:43.000Z","uid":31355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2244246bbc5f3b7b8eab15f2eecf82eaab707c4f","tid":598162,"uid":31355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"屋企有隻布偶女,呢排成日都瀨屎<br />\n佢又唔似肚柯 係柯實屎 但踩到成屋都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日番到屋企見到周地都係屎<br />\n佢又唔係唔識去貓沙盤柯<br />\n搞到好煩惱 每次都要曬成個鐘執<br />\n同幫佢沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲可以教下我點做 希望有方法幫到佢"},{"pid":"339cbbd353c13bfd83e59fadb757b8af801e93fa","tid":598162,"uid":200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"放過隻貓個屎忽啦"},{"pid":"c48caa41a04bff74e23ada4c453fc2611ef09d4f","tid":598162,"uid":166310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:33:10.000Z","msg":"我隻布偶女都試過<br />\n你隻貓幾大? 有可能係唔夠位<br />\n你試下郁一郁貓砂盤個位，個盤既頭尾唔好貼牆，唔好有野頂住"},{"pid":"bd61f306f1eb561f9ec65d8ab375c6dc2151346c","tid":598162,"uid":31355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c48caa41a04bff74e23ada4c453fc2611ef09d4f","tid":598162,"uid":166310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:33:10.000Z","msg":"我隻布偶女都試過<br />\n你隻貓幾大? 有可能係唔夠位<br />\n你試下郁一郁貓砂盤個位，個盤既頭尾唔好貼牆，唔好有野頂住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T07:17:40.000Z","msg":"一歲阿<br />\n但之前都有觀察過佢柯<br />\n都正正常常冇咩野<br />\n我會試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aad2c2c1ee4d30909742a854756141774bc684c","tid":598162,"uid":139270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T17:03:27.000Z","msg":"我果隻都會踩屎架 但係一時時 個廁所都算大...<br />\n是隻蠢貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e392fad89d70e7887b397d46e64fc369effb583","tid":598162,"uid":132918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T17:08:10.000Z","msg":"我果隻細過會踩屎，大過左就好少踩<br />\n加上佢好怕臭，除非忍唔到，隻貓一定係屋企有人先會痾屎。<br />\n屋企人見佢痾完會即清，因為太臭。"},{"pid":"a0f7bd4e042f83ea2bf687f0cc5aa3af976aadea","tid":598162,"uid":144631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"絕左育未？<br />\n有無轉過貓砂？<br />\n砂盤有無轉過位？"}]}